<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 22:08:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>本-格维尔拒绝支持该法案，直到获得内塔尼亚胡安全席位为止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-refuses-to-support-bill-until-given-a-seat-at-netanyahus-security-table/00000190-93dd-d463-abda-ffddef8e0000</link><description>国家安全部长本-格维尔拒绝支持沙斯法案，直到总理将他纳入对战争做出关键决定的“小内阁”</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 20:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-refuses-to-support-bill-until-given-a-seat-at-netanyahus-security-table/00000190-93dd-d463-abda-ffddef8e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导层表示，内塔尼亚胡发表声明后，人质交易的可能性很小</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leadership-says-chances-slim-for-hostage-deal-following-netanyahus-statement/00000190-931d-dfc0-a3f3-bffdcd660000</link><description>加沙以外的哈马斯领导人指出，以色列总理的“原则清单”证明协议几乎没有机会。 加沙的一名官员告诉《国土报》，“内塔尼亚胡支持没有最后期限的谈判，以便赢得时间”，并且“任何人都希望取得突破”生活在幻觉中’</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:57:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leadership-says-chances-slim-for-hostage-deal-following-netanyahus-statement/00000190-931d-dfc0-a3f3-bffdcd660000</guid></item><item><title>以色列派往欧洲反犹太主义极右翼的流氓特使的离奇案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-curious-case-of-israels-rogue-envoy-to-europes-antisemitic-far-right/00000190-92f5-dcf1-afdd-d2f5f2d40000</link><description>许多以色列人感到自己被政府背叛，因为政府未能在 10 月 7 日之前、期间和之后确保他们的安全。散居海外的犹太人现在知道他们的感受。以色列部长背叛了个人和社区的安全</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-curious-case-of-israels-rogue-envoy-to-europes-antisemitic-far-right/00000190-92f5-dcf1-afdd-d2f5f2d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第276天：消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡在谈判代表中划定的休战“红线”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-276-netanyahus-red-lines-for-truce-box-in-negotiators-sources-say/00000190-933e-d1c5-a1d6-bbfe237e0000</link><description>以辛贝特为首的以色列代表团抵达开罗，继续人质释放谈判 ■ 以色列国防军将很快公布其对 10 月 7 日事件的调查结果。 美国 ■ 拜登表示，他对以色列和加沙的计划“非常接近”被执行 ■ 哈马斯高级官员据报道，加沙官员向该组织的政治梯队施压，要求他们接受拜登的停火提议，尽管辛瓦尔表示反对。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-276-netanyahus-red-lines-for-truce-box-in-negotiators-sources-say/00000190-933e-d1c5-a1d6-bbfe237e0000</guid></item><item><title>救赎之路|以色列对哈马斯的战争如何成为加沙犹太人定居点的跳板</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-08/ty-article-static/.premium/israel-seized-26-of-gaza-now-jewish-settlers-see-their-chance/00000190-77cd-d705-a7f5-fffffcbc0000</link><description>以色列国防军已经控制了加沙地带26%的地区，修建基地、铺设道路。以色列的宗教权利已经在朝着其目标前进。这就是以色列士兵眼中的样子</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:57:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-08/ty-article-static/.premium/israel-seized-26-of-gaza-now-jewish-settlers-see-their-chance/00000190-77cd-d705-a7f5-fffffcbc0000</guid></item><item><title>2024年上半年赴以色列旅游人数大幅下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/number-of-tourists-travelling-to-israel-drops-significantly-in-first-half-of-2024/00000190-92be-dcf1-afdd-d2fe0a9a0000</link><description>加沙战争期间，前往以色列的旅游人数下降了 76%，而以色列人仍然渴望出国航班 以色列统计机构报告</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:19:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/number-of-tourists-travelling-to-israel-drops-significantly-in-first-half-of-2024/00000190-92be-dcf1-afdd-d2fe0a9a0000</guid></item><item><title>斯塔默和马克龙本周无法给拜登的一条关键建议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-one-critical-piece-of-advice-starmer-and-macron-cant-give-biden-this-week/00000190-9293-dfc0-a3f3-bef388390000</link><description>政治命运截然不同、选举环境截然不同的三个亲密盟友将于本周在华盛顿举行的北约会议上会面。联盟的未来取决于对美国总统的政治建议，而英法领导人却无法真正提供这些建议</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:42:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-one-critical-piece-of-advice-starmer-and-macron-cant-give-biden-this-week/00000190-9293-dfc0-a3f3-bef388390000</guid></item><item><title>模棱两可的规定让骑警可以自行决定鞭打以色列抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ambiguous-regulations-let-mounted-police-whip-israeli-protesters-at-their-discretion/00000190-9241-d1c5-a1d6-bacd20500000</link><description>在过去的一年半里，马匹和骑警伤害了数十名抗议者。当司法部审问一名涉嫌鞭打抗议者的警官时，警方发布了新规定，允许当骑警意识到自己或公众的安全受到威胁时，可以使用缰绳攻击抗议者。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ambiguous-regulations-let-mounted-police-whip-israeli-protesters-at-their-discretion/00000190-9241-d1c5-a1d6-bacd20500000</guid></item><item><title>厄立特里亚人在特拉维夫南部的斗殴中丧生，这是自去年九月骚乱以来第七人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/eritrean-killed-in-brawl-in-south-tel-aviv-the-seventh-killed-since-riots-last-september/00000190-927c-dfc0-a3f3-befd7fe00000</link><description>厄立特里亚政权支持者和反对者之间出于政治动机的冲突已造成 150 多人受伤。与此同时，耶路撒冷法官上个月裁定，厄立特里亚军队的逃兵可以成为在以色列获得庇护的理由</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 14:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/eritrean-killed-in-brawl-in-south-tel-aviv-the-seventh-killed-since-riots-last-september/00000190-927c-dfc0-a3f3-befd7fe00000</guid></item><item><title>“一个奇迹般的时刻”：以色列极右翼犹太原教旨主义者想要战争、定居点和起义。内塔尼亚胡正在为他们提供便利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-miraculous-time-israels-far-right-fundamentalists-want-war-settlements-and-intifada/00000190-917b-d591-a7ff-fffbc46e0000</link><description>对于像奥里特·斯特罗克和比扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇这样的极右翼弥赛亚定居者部长及其大量选民来说，加沙九个月的战斗还不够。他们感觉到了征服和权力的圣经机会，内塔尼亚胡总理不会公开反对他们。这是两个以色列人之间战争的故事</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 12:45:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-miraculous-time-israels-far-right-fundamentalists-want-war-settlements-and-intifada/00000190-917b-d591-a7ff-fffbc46e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟提出允许以色列古物管理局在西岸开展业务的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/coalition-advances-bill-allowing-israels-antiquities-authority-to-operate-in-west-bank/00000190-91e4-d3a3-ad9a-b3ff1c630000</link><description>该法案的解释性说明称，“毫无疑问，这些地区沉浸在犹太历史中，无论如何，这些发现与巴勒斯坦权力机构没有历史或其他联系。”古物管理局局长反对此举并表示不可行</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 11:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/coalition-advances-bill-allowing-israels-antiquities-authority-to-operate-in-west-bank/00000190-91e4-d3a3-ad9a-b3ff1c630000</guid></item><item><title>“外交炸弹”：以色列侨民部长支持勒庞，以色列外交官愤怒不已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-rallied-behind-le-pen-and-israeli-diplomats-are-livid/00000190-918b-d443-adbe-b1dbca120000</link><description>接受《国土报》采访的以色列外交部官员表示，奇克利部长损害了与法国的关系，其中一位官员表示，他在与欧洲极右翼政党不断发展的关系中完全独立运作</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:14:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-rallied-behind-le-pen-and-israeli-diplomats-are-livid/00000190-918b-d443-adbe-b1dbca120000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：甘茨保持领先内塔尼亚胡，反对派集团有望获得多数席位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/poll-gantz-maintains-lead-over-netanyahu-opposition-bloc-poised-for-majority/00000190-90f8-d99b-a5fc-9ffd227e0000</link><description>反对派集团预计将获得 67 个席位，而内塔尼亚胡的联盟集团预计将获得 53 个席位</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 06:25:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/poll-gantz-maintains-lead-over-netanyahu-opposition-bloc-poised-for-majority/00000190-90f8-d99b-a5fc-9ffd227e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称内塔尼亚胡阻碍人质谈判，呼吁调解人介入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-live/idf-suspicious-target-intercepted-over-red-sea-en-route-to-israel/00000190-904c-de32-a79e-9fdda67f0000</link><description>哈马斯称内塔尼亚胡为停火谈判设置障碍；敦促调解员进行干预 ■ 从以色列北部空旷地区的黎巴嫩土地发射火箭弹 ■ 辛贝特酋长和以色列谈判小组前往开罗会谈 ■ 以色列国防军表示，部队在加沙市近东救济工程处驻地执行任务，为平民建立了安全通道</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 03:23:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-live/idf-suspicious-target-intercepted-over-red-sea-en-route-to-israel/00000190-904c-de32-a79e-9fdda67f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在以色列与哈马斯的谈判中争取时间，押注人质的命运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-approach-to-negotiations-is-to-stall-gambling-on-the-hostages-fate/00000190-8e8e-d591-a7ff-fefeb1570000</link><description>美国对埃及和卡塔尔的压力正推动与哈马斯取得突破。然而，内塔尼亚胡在代表团访问开罗之前采取了一贯的强硬立场。拜登的健康状况可能会转移人们对中东的注意力</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 03:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-approach-to-negotiations-is-to-stall-gambling-on-the-hostages-fate/00000190-8e8e-d591-a7ff-fefeb1570000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与哈马斯重启谈判，公布人质交易“原则清单”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-publishes-list-of-principles-for-hostage-deal-as-talks-with-hamas-renew/00000190-8eb4-d0cb-abb9-feb7f0a00000</link><description>外交消息人士对内塔尼亚胡的声明表示担忧，称总理“限制了自己和谈判团队”，但另一位消息人士指出“谈判中出现了真正的安全担忧”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 19:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-publishes-list-of-principles-for-hostage-deal-as-talks-with-hamas-renew/00000190-8eb4-d0cb-abb9-feb7f0a00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府出人意料地宣布建立以色列第一家阿拉伯文化博物馆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/in-surprise-move-netanyahu-government-announces-israels-first-museum-of-arab-culture/00000190-8dd6-dcf1-afdd-ddf6a0e70000</link><description>以色列北部的 Umm al-Fahm 美术馆的目标之一是向游客介绍巴勒斯坦的叙事，该美术馆将在未来五年内获得 2200 万谢克尔（近 600 万美元），以达到国家博物馆标准</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:50:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/in-surprise-move-netanyahu-government-announces-israels-first-museum-of-arab-culture/00000190-8dd6-dcf1-afdd-ddf6a0e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的阿拉伯公民是否应该应征入伍——不是加入以色列国防军，而是服兵役？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/should-israels-arab-citizens-be-drafted-into-civilian-national-service/00000190-8d98-d591-a7ff-fffaf0780000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡联盟努力解决极端正统犹太人的兵役问题时，另一个主要社区免受以色列国防军征兵的约束：阿拉伯公民。尽管阿拉伯领导人对民用替代方案充满热情，但他们并不相信政府的意图。一位活动人士问道：“这个法西斯政府是否希望将我视为以色列成功故事的一部分？”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:46:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/should-israels-arab-citizens-be-drafted-into-civilian-national-service/00000190-8d98-d591-a7ff-fffaf0780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官在加沙南部被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/israeli-officer-killed-in-southern-gaza/00000190-8e29-d0cb-abb9-fe3bac970000</link><description>来自以色列北部德鲁兹村庄的 25 岁贾拉·易卜拉欣 (Jalaa Ibrahem) 少校周日在加沙地带被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/israeli-officer-killed-in-southern-gaza/00000190-8e29-d0cb-abb9-fe3bac970000</guid></item><item><title>英国新首相与以色列内塔尼亚胡通话，呼吁停火和人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/u-k-s-new-pm-speaks-with-israels-netanyahu-calls-for-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal/00000190-8dca-d591-a7ff-fffa76c90000</link><description>总理基尔·斯塔默表示，他对以色列北部边境的局势感到“担忧” ■ 新当选的总理还与巴勒斯坦总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯进行了交谈</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/u-k-s-new-pm-speaks-with-israels-netanyahu-calls-for-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal/00000190-8dca-d591-a7ff-fffa76c90000</guid></item></channel></rss>